title: Episode 9 - 25 Bars Of Xanax
itunes:title: Episode 9 - 25 Bars Of Xanax
description:
The Doughertys have just been arrested in Walsenburg, Colorado. The siblings are taken to the local hospital for injuries they’ve sustained in their attempt to get away from law Enforcement. Meanwhile, FBI Agents, Pasco County Sheriff’s Detectives and the national media have descended Walsenburg.
